<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        
        /* Header Styles */
        header {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 1rem 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        
        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 30px;
        }
        
        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .nav-links a:hover,
        .nav-links a.active {
            color: #667eea;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .nav-links a.active::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: #667eea;
            border-radius: 1px;
        }
        
        .user-menu {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .cart-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
        }
        
        .cart-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }
        
        /* User Dropdown Styles */
        .user-dropdown {
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .user-avatar {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .user-avatar:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }
        
        .dropdown-menu {
            position: absolute;
            top: 100%;
            right: 0;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            min-width: 280px;
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            z-index: 1000;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        .dropdown-menu.show {
            opacity: 1;
            visibility: visible;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        
        .dropdown-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        
        .avatar-small {
            width: 45px;
            height: 45px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .user-info {
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .user-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }
        
        .user-email {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        .dropdown-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
        }
        
        .dropdown-item:hover {
            background-color: #f8f9ff;
        }
        
        .dropdown-item.logout {
            color: #dc3545;
        }
        
        .dropdown-item.logout:hover {
            background-color: #fff5f5;
        }
        
        .dropdown-menu hr {
            margin: 8px 0;
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        
        /* Auth buttons cho user chưa đăng nhập */
        .auth-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .login-btn {
            background: transparent;
            color: #667eea;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border: 2px solid #667eea;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .login-btn:hover {
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .register-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .register-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }
        
        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 0;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        
        /* Products Section */
        .products-section {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 60px 0;
            margin: 60px 0;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .products-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            padding: 0 30px;
        }
        
        .product-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .product-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        /* ✅ REAL PRODUCT IMAGE STYLES */
        .product-image-wrapper {
            height: 250px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .product-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .product-card:hover .product-image {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        
        /* Fallback emoji style */
        .product-image-emoji {
            height: 250px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #f093fb, #f5576c);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .product-image-emoji::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .product-card:hover .product-image-emoji::before {
            opacity: 1;
        }
        
        .product-info {
            padding: 25px;
        }
        
        .product-brand {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #666;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .product-name {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        
        .product-description {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        
        .product-price {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .product-original-price {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #999;
            text-decoration: line-through;
            margin-left: 8px;
        }
        
        .add-to-cart {
            width: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .add-to-cart:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }
        
        /* ✅ NO DATA MESSAGE */
        .no-data-message {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            color: #666;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin: 20px;
        }
        
        .no-data-message h3 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        /* Call to Action Section */
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 0;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .cta-section h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        
        .cta-section p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        
        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .cta-btn {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .cta-btn.primary {
            background: white;
            color: #667eea;
            border-color: white;
        }
        
        .cta-btn.primary:hover {
            background: #f8f9ff;
        }
        
        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            margin-top: 60px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }
        
        footer p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        /* Flash Messages */
        .flash-messages {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            z-index: 1000;
            max-width: 400px;
        }
        
        .flash-message {
            background: #28a745;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            animation: slideIn 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .flash-message.error {
            background: #dc3545;
        }
        
        .flash-message.warning {
            background: #ffc107;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        @keyframes slideIn {
            from {
                transform: translateX(100%);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                transform: translateX(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
        
        /* Product Modal */
        .modal-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 2000;
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .modal-overlay.show {
            opacity: 1;
            visibility: visible;
        }
        
        .product-modal {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            max-height: 90vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
            transform: scale(0.8);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .modal-overlay.show .product-modal {
            transform: scale(1);
        }
        
        .modal-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        
        .modal-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .modal-close {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: #666;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .modal-close:hover {
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .product-preview {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .product-preview-image {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #f093fb, #f5576c);
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: white;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .product-preview-info {
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .product-preview-name {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .product-preview-price {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #667eea;
        }
        
        .modal-option {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .modal-option label {
            display: block;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .required-star {
            color: #e74c3c;
        }
        
        .option-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(60px, 1fr));
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .option-btn {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .option-btn:hover {
            border-color: #667eea;
            background: #f8f9ff;
        }
        
        .option-btn.selected {
            border-color: #667eea;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .color-option {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 5px;
            border: 3px solid #e0e0e0;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .color-option.selected {
            border-color: #667eea;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        
        .color-red { background: #dc3545; }
        .color-blue { background: #007bff; }
        .color-black { background: #333; }
        .color-white { background: #fff; border-color: #ccc; }
        .color-green { background: #28a745; }
        .color-yellow { background: #ffc107; }
        
        .quantity-selector {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .quantity-btn {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .quantity-btn:hover {
            border-color: #667eea;
            background: #f8f9ff;
        }
        
        .quantity-input {
            width: 60px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .modal-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        
        .modal-btn {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 15px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .modal-btn.primary {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .modal-btn.primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }
        
        .modal-btn.secondary {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            color: #666;
            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        
        .modal-btn.secondary:hover {
            background: #e9ecef;
        }
        
        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-links {
                display: none;
            }
            
            .auth-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 8px;
            }
            
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            .products-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                padding: 0 15px;
            }
            
            .cta-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            
            .dropdown-menu {
                right: -50px;
                min-width: 250px;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                padding: 0 15px;
            }
            
            .hero {
                padding: 60px 0;
            }
            
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .hero p {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
            
            .products-section {
                margin: 30px 0;
                padding: 40px 0;
            }
            
            .section-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Flash Messages -->
    <% if (typeof success !== 'undefined' && success && success.length > 0) { %>
        <div class="flash-messages">
            <div class="flash-message">
                ✅ <%= success %>
            </div>
        </div>
    <% } %>
    
    <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined' && error && error.length > 0) { %>
        <div class="flash-messages">
            <div class="flash-message error">
                ❌ <%= error %>
            </div>
        </div>
    <% } %>

    <header>
        <nav class="container">
            <div class="logo">SportShop</div>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="/" class="<%= currentPage === 'home' ? 'active' : '' %>">Trang chủ</a></li>
                <li><a href="/products" class="<%= currentPage === 'products' ? 'active' : '' %>">Sản phẩm</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about" class="<%= currentPage === 'about' ? 'active' : '' %>">Giới thiệu</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact" class="<%= currentPage === 'contact' ? 'active' : '' %>">Liên hệ</a></li>
            </ul>
            <div class="user-menu">
                <a href="/cart" class="cart-btn">
                    🛒 Giỏ hàng (<%= typeof cartItemCount !== 'undefined' ? cartItemCount : 0 %>)
                </a>
                
                <!-- Hiển thị menu khác nhau dựa trên trạng thái đăng nhập -->
                <% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user) { %>
                    <!-- User đã đăng nhập -->
                    <div class="user-dropdown">
                        <div class="user-avatar" onclick="toggleUserMenu()" title="<%= user.fullName %>">
                            <%= user.initials || user.fullName.charAt(0) %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="dropdown-menu" id="userDropdownMenu">
                            <div class="dropdown-header">
                                <div class="avatar-small">
                                    <%= user.initials || user.fullName.charAt(0) %>
                                </div>
                                <div class="user-info">
                                    <div class="user-name"><%= user.fullName %></div>
                                    <div class="user-email"><%= user.email %></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <hr>
                            <a href="/user/account" class="dropdown-item">
                                <span>🏠</span> Tài khoản của tôi
                            </a>
                            <a href="/user/profile" class="dropdown-item">
                                <span>👤</span> Thông tin cá nhân
                            </a>
                            <a href="/user/orders" class="dropdown-item">
                                <span>📦</span> Đơn hàng
                            </a>
                        
                            <hr>
                            <a href="/auth/logout" class="dropdown-item logout" onclick="return confirm('Bạn có chắc muốn đăng xuất?')">
                                <span>🚪</span> Đăng xuất
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% } else { %>
                    <!-- User chưa đăng nhập -->
                    <div class="auth-buttons">
                        <a href="/auth/login" class="login-btn">🔐 Đăng nhập</a>
                        <a href="/auth/register" class="register-btn">📝 Đăng ký</a>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <section class="hero">
            <h1>Thời Trang Thể Thao Chất Lượng Cao</h1>
            <p>Khám phá bộ sưu tập quần áo thể thao hiện đại, phong cách và thoải mái</p>
        </section>

        <section class="products-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Sản Phẩm Nổi Bật</h2> 
            <div class="products-grid">
                <% if (featuredProducts && featuredProducts.length > 0) { %>
